jobContext:
Provide creative output and direction to ensure the overall vision for the product is achieved;
Lead, recruit, coach, and mentor a team of world-class product designers and user researchers;
Collaborate with members of cross-functional teams and be a champion for user-centered culture and design practices;
Create visually engaging, innovative and functional digital products;
Work closely with product managers, sample department, Merchandiser and QA and department to ensure a cohesive user experience across all products;
Organize teams that can provide design solutions effectively and with excellence across all departments;
Establish metrics and measurable goals to ensure a visibility into design's impact to business;
Identify improvement opportunities within the scope of design and other teams functioning holistically;
Build design culture that encourages innovation while balancing the need for optimization;
Communicate value of design thinking and a customer-first approach to strategy across all areas of the business
